sentence: The All India Mahila Empowerment Party was launched at The Lalit in New Delhi on 12 November 2017 in the presence of important personalities from different fields, including cricketer Mohammed Azharuddin, tennis player Sania Mirza, film stars Suniel Shetty, Bobby Deol, Aftab Shivdaasani, Zeenat Aman, Poonam Dhillon, choreographer Farah Khan, and Urdu poetess Lata Haya.
